descriptionHtml:
[b]Players home.[/b]

[b]TINTAGEL[/b] has it's own world space.

Entrance to TINTAGEL "Portal Gem Door" is located at The Guardian Stone,see picture for more info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.


[b]Cleaned with TES5Edit.

[/b][b]Requirements:[/b] Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[b]Installation:[/b] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually then you have to extract it into your data                       file for Skyrim.[b]
[/b][b]
Unistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.


[b]CREDITS:[/b] Many thanks to arrioch for his permission to use his "Arri's Snow Elf Ruins Retexture"


I hope you enjoy the home if so please endorse.


My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
